               <p>SIXTH DAY, TUESDAY, SEPTEMBER 16.</p>
               <p>Middlesex Cases, Second Jury,</p>
               <p>Before Mr. Recorder.</p>
               <p>1031. 
               
                  <persName id="t18230910-58-defend708" type="defendantName">
                     JOHN 
                     FARRIER
                  <interp inst="t18230910-58-defend708" type="surname" value="FARRIER"></interp>
